										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The holiday season is the busiest marketing time of the year, and many small business owners find themselves scrambling to create campaigns, emails, social content, and ads.</p>
<p>This is where AI can become your secret weapon. With the right prompts, you can generate compelling holiday marketing content in <em>minutes</em> instead of hours.</p>
<p>That said, generic AI prompts won&#8217;t cut it. You need holiday-specific prompts tailored to your target audience for maximum relevancy.</p>
<p>Below, you&#8217;ll find actionable holiday marketing AI prompts for small businesses that are organized by channelâ€”ready for you to customize and use right away.</p>
