<p>This is exactly what the menâ€™s apparel brand Chubbies does with its loyalty programs. In addition to making a purchase and creating an account, customers can also earn extra points for leaving a review. Itâ€™s a win-win situationâ€”customers earn points, and you gather UGC content.</p>
