<p>BÃ‰IS is a chic luggage brand that created an <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/interactive-content">interactive</a> luggage â€˜car washâ€™ experience that got people waiting in lines and sharing videos, which helped them rack up thousands of views on TikTok.</p>
