<h3>7. Use UGC on your homepage</h3>
<p>Your website is one of the first touchpoints for your customers, and your homepage is your virtual â€œdoormat,â€ welcoming customers. So if you want to highlight UGC, whether thatâ€™s customer photos and videos or reviews and testimonials, your website homepage can be the perfect stage to show off all that real, authentic content that makes your brand feel human.</p>
<p>Brookfield Residential is a real estate developer that showcases customer reviews on its homepage using a third-party, independent reviews platform to boost credibility.</p>
